t laws within its education center. Additionally, if you sign up for its credit repair services you get in-person help and regular emails with credit tips.","When you register for credit repair with Veracity, you get assigned a personal case advisor to help you throughout your time with the company. This is helpful for people who like to build a relationship and feel comfortable with someone when they’re discussing their finances and their credit. If you need to check your progress after-hours, you can also use the online portal to see your credit repair progress.","Veracity charges the lowest monthly fee in our review of credit repair companies. That makes the cost for six months of credit repair service the second cheapest in our review. However, one downside to the costs is the relatively low couples discount offered by this company. If you sign up with a spouse you will only save an average of 5 percent for six months of service.","This company scored low in our reviews because you need to sign up for its higher levels of service in order to dispute negative items with your creditors. Otherwise, your disputes can only go to the credit bureaus and removed items have a chance of reappearing because they weren’t removed from the creditors’ records.","This company does offer monthly credit monitoring, which is a great way for you to track your progress and make sure nothing else is lowering your credit scores. However, this monitoring is also only available with the higher level of Veracity Platinum service. The best credit repair companies bundle this service with their regular monthly fees."]},"id":"297ba9c9-f1de-4ac4-b2fd-174e70dabe67","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"d5043b6b-f816-404b-ba47-54e3760a9acb","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Veracity Credit Solutions offers credit repair services at the lowest monthly cost of all the companies we reviewed. However, that low monthly fee only gets you access to basic services and doesn’t include monthly credit monitoring or the ability to dispute negative items with creditors. If you have a lot of negative items, especially items from creditors, you should look to one of the other services in our credit repair services review. If you only have a few negative items being reported by the credit bureaus, though, this service may work well for you."]},"id":"e7f37e4c-e44c-4fdc-826b-dea025f45d1a","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_49598","url":"/veracity-credit-consultants-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"ryan-brown","url":"/author/ryan-brown","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Ryan Brown","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"HR3J5H9LhLCfWmFnumxwPW","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-05-21T17:35:16Z","datePublished":"2010-05-21T17:35:16Z","name":"Veracity Credit Consultants","synopsis":"Veracity Credit Solutions is a credit repair company that specializes in helping people remove inaccurate, negative items from their credit reports.","review":{"rating":67,"verdict":"If monthly cost is the most important factor for you in choosing credit repair, this company may be your best choice. However, if you want more than basic credit repair features, there are better options.","pros":["This company has the lowest monthly cost of any credit repair company we reviewed."],"cons":["You have to sign up for Veracity&#8217;s higher level of service to have this company contact creditors."]},"strapline":"Veracity Credit Solutions is a credit repair company that specializes in helping people remove inaccurate, negative items from their credit reports.","language":"en","dateModified":"2010-05-21T17:35:16Z","id":"wsGvfAHg6Ajt5b68qRduXh","meta":{"title":"Veracity Credit Consultants Credit Repair Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"Veracity Credit Solutions offers the lowest monthly fee of any credit repair company in our review. Read the full review for